WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.196
Beyond simple transactional convenience, customers eagerly prefer purchasing through this

00:00:04.196 --> 00:00:08.392
route because it radically consolidates corporate expenditure. It entirely removes

00:00:08.392 --> 00:00:12.588
immense bureaucratic friction by centralizing procurement, finance, and legal approvals

00:00:12.588 --> 00:00:16.783
into one trusted pipeline, dramatically reducing standard regulatory red tape

00:00:16.783 --> 00:00:20.979
and accelerating the time to value for the marketing teams

00:00:20.979 --> 00:00:25.175
who desperately need our technology.
